isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-auction-shenzhen-land-plot-with-loss-making-reserve-price-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>壳牌将新加坡炼油厂和石油化工资产出售给 Chandra Asri 和 Glencore</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shell-sell-singapore-refinery-petrochemical-assets-chandra-asri-glencore-2024-05-08/</link><description>壳牌周三表示，已同意将其在亚洲主要石油中心新加坡的炼油厂和石化资产出售给印度尼西亚化学品公司 Chandra Asri 与瑞士矿业和大宗商品贸易商嘉能可 (Glencore) 的合资企业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 06:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shell-sell-singapore-refinery-petrochemical-assets-chandra-asri-glencore-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国四月份出口可能恢复增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-swung-back-growth-april-2024-05-08/</link><description>中国的出口继3月份大幅萎缩后，可能在4月份恢复增长，但由于工厂主正在努力应对海外需求疲软和产能过剩导致售价下降的情况，预计出口增速将较为温和。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 05:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-swung-back-growth-april-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>宝马称成本和二手车价格低将影响2024年税前利润</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-q1-automotive-margin-falls-high-costs-persist-2024-05-08/</link><description>宝马周三表示，由于研发、制造和人员成本上升，预计今年税前利润将小幅下降，二手车价格下降也是造成下降的原因之一。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 05:34:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-q1-automotive-margin-falls-high-costs-persist-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>塔利班否认巴基斯坦声称阿富汗轰炸机参与对中国水坝工程师的致命袭击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taliban-reject-pakistans-claim-afghan-bomber-involved-deadly-attack-chinese-dam-2024-05-08/</link><description>塔利班国防部周三驳回了巴基斯坦有关阿富汗人参与袭击中国工程师的指控，因为邻国之间的关系因不安全局势加剧而恶化。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 05:28:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taliban-reject-pakistans-claim-afghan-bomber-involved-deadly-attack-chinese-dam-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国考虑将越南提升为“市场经济”地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-weighs-upgrade-vietnam-market-economy-status-2024-05-08/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登将越南拉近为战略盟友的努力将与他周三获得工会工人投票的愿望发生正面冲突，因为美国商务部将听取有关是否将越南指定为“市场经济”的证词。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 05:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-weighs-upgrade-vietnam-market-economy-status-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>随着美联储利率路径的思考，亚洲股市下滑，美元上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-08/</link><description>亚洲股市周三下跌，尽管美国国债收益率较低，但美元仍在上涨，因为市场对美国政策制定者的信号和美联储利率走势的经济数据的评估不一。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 02:25:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称其军队已准备好应对中国围绕新总统就职典礼采取的行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-its-military-is-ready-china-moves-around-new-presidents-inaugural-2024-05-08/</link><description>台湾国防部副部长周三表示，台湾军方已做好准备，应对中国在当选总统赖清德本月晚些时候就职期间可能采取的任何行动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 02:23:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-its-military-is-ready-china-moves-around-new-presidents-inaugural-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>在快速老龄化的中国，数百万农民工无力退休</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rapidly-ageing-china-millions-cant-afford-retire-2024-05-08/</link><description>上世纪末涌入中国城市的一代人，建设基础设施、管理工厂，使中国成为世界上最大的出口国，现在他们面临着晚年生活水平急剧下降的风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 02:04:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rapidly-ageing-china-millions-cant-afford-retire-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>美元上涨；日元贬值引发日本警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-regains-momentum-yen-struggles-2024-05-08/</link><description>美元周三保持坚挺，收复了因今年美联储降息重新押注而造成的部分损失，而日元则连续第三天走弱，令投资者对东京干预的风险保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 01:17:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-regains-momentum-yen-struggles-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道称，埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 提议在 4 月份访问中国期间在中国推出机器人出租车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-may-support-teslas-domestic-testing-demonstration-robotaxis-says-media-2024-05-08/</link><description>据官方支持的《中国日报》周三援引消息人士的话报道，埃隆·马斯克在最近访问中国期间提议在中国测试特斯拉的先进驾驶辅助方案，将其部署在机器人出租车上。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 01:05:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-may-support-teslas-domestic-testing-demonstration-robotaxis-says-media-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>通过现场检查，中国加大对本土IPO候选人的审查力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/with-onsite-inspections-china-dials-up-scrutiny-local-market-ipo-hopefuls-2024-05-08/</link><description>据十名消息人士透露，中国监管机构正在审查旧的商业交易，甚至高管的个人银行账户，同时加大对有望首次公开募股的公司的检查力度，以减缓新融资的步伐并提振二级市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 00:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/with-onsite-inspections-china-dials-up-scrutiny-local-market-ipo-hopefuls-2024-05-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>